<para style="p">A prayer of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Listen, Yahweh, and answer me,</para>

<para style="q1">for I am poor and oppressed.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Protect me, for I am loyal;</para>

<para style="q1">my God, save your servant who trusts in you.</para>
